fields.title: Yearly Bundle - Gold
fields.description: 12 month fully comprehensive membership - includes full travel expenses for club shows and sparring, 5 x family tickets for all events, and full set of club apparel and boxing gear. Great for young prospects!

fields.title: Yearly Bundle - Silve
fields.description: 12 month membership including club apparel and boxing gear. Hoodie, t-shirt, sweatpants, gloves, handwraps and mouthguard all included. Great for returning members!

fields.title: Yearly Bundle - Bronze
fields.description: 12 month membership. Club apparel and training gear must be purchased separately ahead of club shows and club sparring. Great for beginners and first timers!

fields.title: Quarterly Bundle - Gold
fields.description: 3 month membership for 36 sessions - includes technical sessions on Mondays and Wednesdays, as well as our doghouse sparring sessions on Sunday mornings.

fields.title: Quarterly Bundle - Silver
fields.description: 3 month membership for 24 sessions - includes technical sessions on Mondays and Wednesdays. This package does not include our doghouse sparring sessions on Sunday mornings.

fields.title: Monthly Bundle - Gold
fields.description: 1 month membership for 12 sessions - includes technical sessions on Mondays and Wednesdays, as well as our doghouse sparring sessions on Sunday mornings.

fields.title: Monthly Bundle - Silver
fields.description: 1 month membership for 8 sessions - includes technical sessions on Mondays and Wednesdays. This package does not include our doghouse sparring sessions on Sunday mornings.
